        "start": "0:01:15.84",
        "end": "0:01:19.6"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "text": "The pandemic, which to be fair delayed a lot of things, delayed plans to start building the venue and also drove up construction costs.",
    "confidence": 0.9098,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
