        "adjustedStart": "0:03:47.56",
        "adjustedEnd": "0:03:53.44",
        "start": "0:03:47.56",
        "end": "0:03:53.44"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 38,
    "text": "The Bolshoi Ice Dome, built for 2014, hosted games as early as April 2013 and held an entire tournament in the December preceding the Olympics.",
    "confidence": 0.9199,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
      {
        "adjustedStart": "0:03:53.84",
        "adjustedEnd": "0:04:02.12",
        "start": "0:03:53.84",
        "end": "0:04:02.12"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 39,
    "text": "But in December of 2025, not only were the Santa Julia Arena test games cancelled, presumably due to the place not being built yet, the NHL Board of Governors threatened to pull NHL players out of the Olympics if the ice wasn't safe to play on.",
    "confidence": 0.8587,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
