        "start": "0:04:02.28",
        "end": "0:04:14.16"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 40,
    "text": "Not that the players seem to care, but it's not up to them.",
    "confidence": 0.8221,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
      {
        "adjustedStart": "0:04:14.4",
        "adjustedEnd": "0:04:16.56",
        "start": "0:04:14.4",
        "end": "0:04:16.56"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 41,
    "text": "And to be clear here, the NHL didn't want to pull players.",
    "confidence": 0.8375,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
      {
        "adjustedStart": "0:04:16.56",
        "adjustedEnd": "0:04:19.84",
        "start": "0:04:16.56",
        "end": "0:04:19.84"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 42,
    "text": "In fact, when word got out about how not built to the arena was, the NHL sent some of their top ice technicians over to Italy to pull this thing together.",
    "confidence": 0.9084,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
