        "start": "0:04:37.84",
        "end": "0:04:41.48"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 45,
    "text": "The Zamboni ramp was just two days old, and the first Test game was delayed by 5:00-ish minutes to repair a hole in the ice, reportedly part of a wider soft spot in front of one of the Nets.",
    "confidence": 0.8518,
    "speakerId": 1,
    "language": "en-US",
    "instances": [
      {
        "adjustedStart": "0:04:41.56",
        "adjustedEnd": "0:04:50.68",
        "start": "0:04:41.56",
        "end": "0:04:50.68"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": 46,
    "text": "Over the course of three days, the ice held up and there were no further delays for hole patching.",
    "confidence": 0.8662,
